:0,"replyTime":"2020-10-23T23:09:07.000Z","msg":"黃藍就唔知，黑店一間"},{"pid":"a10f3a75d0348ef3e0c23d3ba9a14407d91c9c4f","tid":2255760,"uid":5737,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-24T00:22:02.000Z","msg":"個乜鳩箱<br />\n成堆簡體字都夠膽拎出黎買<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f8c095d9c88361104722bf0324fa7ee6ff745598","tid":2255760,"uid":199592,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-24T00:42:26.000Z","msg":"之前有人喺連登sell話又快又黃（一定係媒），傻撚咗落咗單，佢哋貨源都幾肯定係淘寶嚟<br />\n<br />\n1.過咗兩三個星期都唔出貨，嗰陣時我趕往用已經喺第到買到正品，佢同我第到買嗰件係兩種質素<br />\n2.同一件貨香港街鋪買一般入外國版，佢零零舍舍賣中國版（有查過）<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />（不過都係咁先發現中國貨係真係劣質啲 唔係rumour嚟）<br />\n3.啲膠有啲黑色一點點，表面有啲塵末抹都抹唔甩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n聽講係pepehk定唔知邊間人血老闆開，好後悔好撚嬲點解無退貨俾佢賺咗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"67b574ca9bd4d59443d7e255fed5bb01fee1617f","tid":2255760,"uid":135740,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-24T00:56:05.000Z","msg":"你叫支持荃扣里班撚屌入黎講啦<br />\n<br />\n黃店賣淘寶已經合理化哂啦<br />\n<br />\n我點解唔直接淘寶要俾你班黃店抽水呀<br />\n<br />\n靠你班黃店捐錢我不如直接捐俾612?"},{"pid":"d7ee96e45115a068a3d3d1af86e746506231dc22","tid":2255760,"uid":374954,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-24T00:57:54.000Z","msg":"我之前差啲買咗，<a href=\"http://呢間好似係以前嘅Pepe.hk\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2F%E5%91%A2%E9%96%93%E5%A5%BD%E4%BC%BC%E4%BF%82%E4%BB%A5%E5%89%8D%E5%98%85Pepe.hk&d=Z0jJ2Ci5UPqU8nDHOGo4vCaGrLhPWbn%2F%2Bskqqi57m1s%3D&h=d8a57543\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">呢間好似係以前嘅Pepe.hk</a>，<a href=\"http://識人話Pepe.hk\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2F%E8%AD%98%E4%BA%BA%E8%A9%B1Pepe.hk&d=Z0jJ2Ci5UPqU8nDHOGo4vCaGrLhPWbn%2F%2Bskqqi57m1s%3D&h=6f2d93ac\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">識人話Pepe.hk</a>之前比晒＄又話無貨，之後又退番＄，網民又話人血饅頭，所以唔敢買<br />\n之後我揀咗買同人辦館(黃店)，仲有書賣㗎，野食香港台灣日本泰國都有，可以去睇下(之前全民感謝日同人辦館都有參與。"}]}